consider a file name ReadMe.md and contain a sentences ,
a word 'repo' is mentioned in it .

let us check this word using command 'grep'

cmd goes like this - > grep 'repo' ReadMe.md

above command will print all  the sentence  which includes word ' repo' 

if the word doesn't present it doesn't print anything


